long_description: Interested in the intersection of medicine and technology?

ADI will be hosting a medical technology tech trek with two events:

(11AM - 12PM)
1) A tour of the Columbia Nursing Simulation Center
Take a behind the scenes look at Columbia's new simulation center helping doctors in training reduce medical errors. Learn more about the center here: http://on.mktw.net/2tqmIJQ

(12PM - 1:30PM)
(Break/Lunch)

(1:30PM - 2:30PM)
2) A special tour of the new Columbia Medical Center building (see event cover photo). We'll be getting a tour with staff from the new center to learn how Columbia is using the latest technologies to advance medical research. 

This is part of an ADI series looking into opportunities in technology that are not based on Software Engineering.

