**********************
We will be following up with emails about further event/logistical details. Unfortunately, we cannot accept everyone for this event and will use a random lottery to decide who can attend. 

We'll likely be traveling on Columbia's shuttle (free with your CU/BCID) , but if you would need a Metrocard to attend, email will@adicu.com

We will be leaving promptly from the Broadway & 116th gates at 10:30am and returning to campus at 3:00pm.

Failure to show up the day of will result in a ban for all future ADI tech treks.